<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Isaac_Asimov%27s_Galactic_Empire_Series" title="Isaac Asimov's Galactic Empire Series" class="mw-redirect">Isaac Asimov's Galactic Empire Series</a></div>
