<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Naked_Sun" title="The Naked Sun">The Naked Sun</a></i> (1957), <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0553293397" class="internal">ISBN 0-553-29339-7</a> (second Elijah Baley SF-crime novel)</li>
